    "title": "A simple solution to a dire problem.",
    "description": "Always incendiary. Each trigger pull fires 10 shots arranged as 2 rows of 5, consuming 6 ammo per shot. Increased damage and magazine size, but reduced fire rate and reload speed. While scoped, it fires in DAHL burst mode. With Mouthwash equipped it gains +200% damage; for Salvador, holding Toothpick in the left hand can pass this bonus to the right-hand weapon. In Writhing Deep, equipping Retainer also grants movement speed and jump height bonuses."
  },
